title: Tomaso Albinoni, Op. 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 9 & 10
description:
Tomaso Giovanni Albinoni (1671 - 1751

Op. 1 - Sonate a tre
Op. 2 - Sinfonie e Concerti a cinque
Op. 3 - Balletti a tre
Op. 4 - Cantate da camera a voce sola
Op. 5 - Concerti a cinque
Op. 6 - Trattenimenti armonici per camera
Op. 7 - Concerti a cinque
Op. 9 - Concerti a cinque
Op. 10 - Concerti a cinque

Performed by: Parnassi musici, Insieme Strumentale di Roma, Ensemble Benedetto Marcello, I Musici, The Locatelli Trio, I Solisti Veneti
File format: mp3, FLAC

Notes: Albinoni's opus 8 has apparently never been recorded. The only version of his unpublished opus 11 (the manuscript itself) was destroyed in the Allied bombing of Dresden in 1945.
